Type: Package
Title: generate and process geometric shapes
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: person("Steffen", "Ehrmann", email = "steffen@funroll-loops.de",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2958-0796"))
Description: The geomTools package provides a simplified approach to generating
    and manipulating geometries at vertex level. Vertices are stored in tables 
    (and not lists) and can simply be transformed into spatial objects. 
